                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "Calcium carbonate is prescribed for a client with hypocalcemia. How would the nurse instruct the client to take the medication?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nCalcium carbonate tablets would be taken with a full glass of water 30 to 60 minutes after meals; therefore, the remaining options are incorrect.\n\nTest-Taking Strategy:\nFocus on the subject, method of administration of calcium carbonate. Eliminate options 1 and 3 because they are comparable or alike with regard to time frames. For the remaining options, eliminate the option of every 4 hours because calcium is usually administered daily or twice a day.\n",
                        "id": "7cddb25de7044502ad032754d5044999",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "1624bcc21ae7481585ff88fd70a8de05",
                                "content": "Take the medication at bedtime."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "841308cb5314481fafe5b9157dfde890",
                                "content": "Take the medication in the morning with breakfast."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "acd1e09af3cc450ca18f02fcdf02c024",
                                "content": "Lie down for 30 minutes after taking the medication."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "66ad359c2ad64953ab06f315426de6b6",
                                "content": "Take the medication with a full glass of water after rising in the morning."
                            }
                        ],
