                        "type": "0",
                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "Alendronate is prescribed for a client with osteoporosis, and the nurse is providing instructions on administration of the medication. Which instruction would the nurse provide?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nPrecautions need to be taken with the administration of alendronate to prevent gastrointestinal adverse effects (especially esophageal irritation) and to increase absorption of the medication. The medication needs to be taken with a full glass of water after rising in the morning. The client would not eat or drink anything for 30 minutes following administration and needs to not lie down after taking the medication.\n\nTest-Taking Strategy:\nFocus on the subject, the administration of alendronate. Recalling that this medication can cause esophageal irritation will direct you to the correct option.",
                        "id": "943ad33eb4a64cb9b5135beb6247c0ad",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "b4a3e733b9334be3aef5477208bd2760",
                                "content": "\"I need to take the tablet an hour after lunch.\""
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "794f19b5f8674a2499a557fb73a1288a",
                                "content": "\"I would swallow the tablet whole with toast at breakfast.\""
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "dfb0671e05174b43ae0240f82b5f4cc7",
                                "content": "\"I would crush the tablet and take it with applesauce at breakfast.\""
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "fd0310ffb14848fcb4f61171c9205fa4",
                                "content": "\"I would cut the tablet in half and take it with ice cream after dinner.\""
